{"tid":2100584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加熱煙獲美國FDA認可  為風險改良煙草產品","createTime":"2020-07-09T07:02:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T14:21:26.000Z","uid":315643,"like":16,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"93ddfca309104f299be70e4a39c8c711b4c0f0a8","tid":2100584,"uid":315643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T07:02:33.000Z","msg":"香港政府仲係府一刀切，禁哂加熱煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n汁: <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-08-2020/64294\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F07-08-2020%2F64294&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmiWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=0d3c85cf\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-08-2020/64294</a><br />\n<br />\n美國食品藥品管理局（FDA）公布，批准菲利普莫里斯國際公司（Philip Morris）研發的加熱煙草產品IQOS，作為「風險改良煙草產品」（Modified risk tobacco products, MRTP），進行銷售。 <br />\n<br />\nFDA煙草產品中心負責人Mitch Zeller表示，FDA是要透過業界申請風險改良煙草產品的過程，確保消費者了解到，使用降低風險或減少接觸有害物質的煙草產品，是有科學證據的支持。 <br />\n<br />\nMitch Zeller引述申請者提交數據表示，使用IQOS可以幫助成癮的成年吸煙者，擺脫傳統燃燒香煙，減少產生有害化學物質的接觸，但前提是必需完全轉換使用。<br />\n<br />\n 他又指說，有關產品獲FDA認可主要是產品僅用加熱，沒有燃燒煙草，所產生的煙霧相比之下，大幅減少有害及潛在有害化學物質的產生，顯著減少人體接觸15種特定有害和可能有害化學物質。 <br />\n<br />\nFDA將密切監視消費者如何使用IQOS，去確定有關產品是否符合以上所指，並確定不會引起包括目前非吸煙者去使用，特別是青少年。 <br />\n<br />\n香港報販協會冀望政府應正視加熱煙需求，盡快讓持牌商販售賣有關產品，保障青少年及消費者，同時打擊黑市買賣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/202007/44872968_10218325191229578_6754774085227511808_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F202007%2F44872968_10218325191229578_6754774085227511808_n.jpg&h=9bbc4f46&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"22b60da7325023956855ef576d26fa68637bfbc6","tid":2100584,"uid":94828,"like":36,"dislike":13,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T07:05:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e3de1a1a1c906ee7e88e41f172432c0203804dfe","tid":2100584,"uid":51271,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T07:08:14.000Z","msg":"支那唔識做加熱煙，所以ban"},{"pid":"cac9daec162ce393a2ce2e75899279a0a1085bbf","tid":2100584,"uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e3de1a1a1c906ee7e88e41f172432c0203804dfe","tid":2100584,"uid":51271,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T07:08:14.000Z","msg":"支那唔識做加熱煙，所以ban"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T07:09:53.000Z","msg":"直頭化學野，做壞曬成個行業<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a59c07ea4fac95ea8366b01119e9fa15f03e182","tid":2100584,"uid":315643,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"22b60da7325023956855ef576d26fa68637bfbc6","tid":2100584,"uid":94828,"like":36,"dislike":13,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T07:05:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T07:11:40.000Z","msg":"無咗啲臭大陸煙味已經好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39eab03ffc25ad06818de89f0e27c13a6ad7fbc7","tid":2100584,"uid":332804,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"e3de1a1a1c906ee7e88e41f172432c0203804dfe","tid":2100584,"uid":51271,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T07:08:14.000Z","msg":"支那唔識做加熱煙，所以ban"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T07:12:26.000Z","msg":"中共一年收好多煙稅，梗係唔會比人搞煙草個市。"},{"pid":"3f0b07bb9d365f71b8b15de232b33f7613c6a156","tid":2100584,"uid":76216,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T07:14:10.000Z","msg":"唔應該食煙"},{"pid":"e2088440ff1c8e810dc3a7e10842bd030d8446c0","tid":2100584,"uid":54550,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"39eab03ffc25ad06818de89f0e27c13a6ad7fbc7","tid":2100584,"uid":332804,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"e3de1a1a1c906ee7e88e41f172432c0203804dfe","tid":2100584,"uid":51271,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"ci